PRO Lifetime Warranty
At PRO we have a simple mission: To work together with the best people in the world to make the best products in the world. And we are so confident about the quality of our products that from today we can offer you a lifetime warranty.*

Over And Over Again. And Again.
We test our products under extreme conditions to meet the highest demands of any rider. Our components are tested to a minimum of 110% of industry standards. And you can benefit from our intensive testing.

* Based on an expected lifetime of 10 years.
